name: Get Out of My Way I'm Trying to Eat You
name_original: Get Out of My Way I'm Trying to Eat You
description:
You play as a box that gets eaten a lot and likes to ignore the laws of momentum. Walljump, screenwrap, and die a lot through 70 levels in 7 unique worlds. It's pretty hard.

Controls:

Arrow keys + Spacebar = move and jump

Up = select level (when level select is unlocked)
